# CODEOWNERS - Automatic PR Reviewer Assignment
#
# This file defines code ownership for automatic reviewer assignment.
# When a pull request modifies files matching these patterns,
# the specified users/teams are automatically requested as reviewers.
#
# Syntax: pattern @username @team
# See: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Default: All files owned by repository owners
# This ensures all PRs (including @copilot-generated) get reviewed
* @owner

# Knowledge base - require review from documentation team
/docs/knowledge/ @owner @docs-team

# GitHub configurations - require review from DevOps
/.github/ @owner @devops-team

# Critical infrastructure files
/package.json @owner @devops-team
/tsconfig.json @owner @devops-team
/.gitignore @owner

# Note: Replace @owner, @docs-team, @devops-team with actual GitHub usernames/teams
# Example: * @alice @bob @engineering-team
